{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"註解","mdn_url":"/zh-TW/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Guide/Control_flow_and_error_handling_74154e098f4b1e7026df3945ceb0fa4a","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"註解","title":"註解","isH3":true,"content":"<p>註解是作者用來解釋 Script 在做什麼的標記符號。註解會被解譯器忽略。JavaScript 支援 Java 和 C++ 形式的註解︰</p>\n<ul> <li>單行註解是在前面加上兩個斜線 (//)。</li> <li>多行註解是在前面加上 /* 並在尾端加上 */。</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>範例</strong><br>\n以下範例示範這兩種註解︰</p>\n<pre class=\"notranslate\">// 這是單行註解。\n\n/* 這是多行註解。不管是什麼長度都可以，你也\n可以在任何你喜歡的地方使用。 */\n</pre>\n<div class=\"noinclude\" id=\"sect1\">\n<p></p><ul class=\"prev-next\">\n    <li><a class=\"button minimal\" href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/JavaScript/教學/物件的操作語法\">« 前頁</a></li>\n    <li><a class=\"button minimal\" href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/JavaScript/教學/例外處理語法\">次頁  »</a></li>\n</ul><p></p>\n</div>"}}],"toc":[],"summary":"註解是作者用來解釋 Script 在做什麼的標記符號。註解會被解譯器忽略。JavaScript 支援 Java 和 C++ 形式的註解︰","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"locale":"en-US","title":"Control flow and error handling","native":"English (US)"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-tw/conflicting/web/javascript/guide/control_flow_and_error_handling_74154e098f4b1e7026df3945ceb0fa4a","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-tw/conflicting/web/javascript/guide/control_flow_and_error_handling_74154e098f4b1e7026df3945ceb0fa4a/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-TW/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Guide","title":"陣列的運用"},{"uri":"/zh-TW/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Guide/Control_flow_and_error_handling_74154e098f4b1e7026df3945ceb0fa4a","title":"註解"}],"pageTitle":"註解 | MDN","noIndexing":true}}